{
    "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
    "$id": "kabegame://provider/v0.7",
    "title": "Kabegame Provider Definition",
    "description": "螢ｰ譏主ｼ・Provider 窶・霍ｯ蠕・釜蜿 ﾃ・ImageQuery 雍｡迪ｮ ﾃ・蜉ｨ諤∵椢荳ｾ縲りｯｦ扈・ｯｭ荵芽ｧ・cocs/provider-dsl/RULES.md縲・n\n荳・Rust trait Provider 蟇ｹ鮨・\n  query   竊・apply_query   闃らせ蟇ｹ邏ｯ遘ｯ ImageQuery 逧・ｴ｡迪ｮ(謌・delegate 蟋疲汚蜿ｦ荳 provider)\n  list    竊・list_children 髱呎∝ｭ鈴擇驥・/ 蜉ｨ諤・SQL / 蜉ｨ諤・delegate 蟄占鰍轤ｹ譫壻ｸｾ\n  resolve 竊・get_child     豁｣蛻呵ｧ｣譫仙黒荳ｪ蟄占鰍轤ｹ\n\nChildEntry 讓｡蝙・\n  { name: string, provider?: ProviderInvocation, meta?: any }\n  - meta 荳ｺ莉ｻ諢・JSON, 隸ｦ隗・RULES.md ﾂｧ4.5(蟄礼ｬｦ荳ｲ=SQL 謌匁ｨ｡譚ｿ; 蟇ｹ雎｡/謨ｰ扈・譬・㍼=逶ｴ謗･菴應ｸｺ meta)\n  - provider 蜿ｯ郛ｺ逵・窶・蠖灘燕螻ゆｸ肴撃荳句ｱ・provider\n\n蜻ｽ蜷咲ｩｺ髣ｴ(Java 蛹・｣取ｼ):\n  鬘ｶ螻・namespace 蟄玲ｮｵ, 蠖｢螯・'kabegame' / 'kabegame.plugin' / 'pixiv'\n  蜈ｨ螻蜷・= <namespace>.<name>; 蜷・namespace 蜀・provider 莠堤嶌蠑慕畑逕ｨ simple name\n  隗｣譫占ｧ・・: 蠖灘燕 namespace 竊・辷ｶ namespace 竊・... 竊・root\n  ProviderInvocation.provider 蜿ｯ蜀・simple name 謌也ｻ晏ｯｹ 'a.b.c.name'\n\n蛻､蛻ｫ遲也払:\n  - Query 莠呈箕: delegate 竓・(from/join/where/fields/order/offset/limit)\n  - StaticListEntry 逕ｨ ProviderInvocation 莠梧・ byName 竓・Empty\n  - Resolve 逕ｨ ProviderInvocation 荳画・ byName 竓・byDelegate 竓・Empty (7b 襍ｷ byDelegate 螟肴ｴｻ, payload 荳ｺ ProviderCall)\n  - List entry 逕ｱ key 譏ｯ蜷ｦ蜷ｫ ${...} 蛻､蛻ｫ 髱呎・/ 蜉ｨ諤―n  - DynamicListEntry 謨ｰ謐ｮ貅蝉ｺ呈箕: sql 竓・delegate\n  - order 蠖｢諤・ 謨ｰ扈・菴咲ｽｮ螳壼ｺ・ 竓・{all:...} 蜈ｨ螻謖・ｻ､(莠碁我ｸ)\n\n6e 襍ｷ: query.delegate / list dynamic delegate 蟄玲ｮｵ邀ｻ蝙倶ｸｺ ProviderCall { provider, properties? }; 荳榊・譏ｯ霍ｯ蠕・｡ｨ霎ｾ蠑・(PathExpr 謨ｴ荳ｪ蛻髯､)縲１rovider 譏ｯ path-unaware 逧・窶・蠑慕畑蜈ｶ螳・provider 襍ｰ namespace 體ｾ + name + properties, 荳肴ｷｷ蜈･霍ｯ蠕・ｦょｿｵ縲・n\nDelegate 蟇ｹ遘ｰ霓ｬ蜿・(7b 襍ｷ荳牙､・ｯｹ鮨・:\n  - query.delegate         竊・target.apply_query(current, ctx)  ; 蛟溽岼譬・噪 contrib 蜈･ composed\n  - list[<dyn>].delegate   竊・target.list(composed, ctx)        ; 隹・岼譬・噪 list 蜿・children 蠎丞・\n  - resolve[].delegate     竊・target.resolve(name, composed, ctx); 謚雁ｽ灘燕 segment 逧・resolve 蜀ｳ螳壽揀霓ｬ扈咏岼譬Ⅸn豈丞､・payload 驛ｽ譏ｯ ProviderCall, 豌ｸ霑・path-unaware縲・n\nContribQuery 諡ｼ謗･隸ｭ荵・\n  fields  竊・邏ｯ遘ｯ蛻ｰ SELECT; 逕ｨ as + in_need 隗｣蜀ｳ蜀ｲ遯―n  from    竊・cascading-replace(豕ｨ諢・ from 荳榊ｺ泌・蠏・JOIN, 隗・RULES.md ﾂｧ3.1)\n  join    竊・邏ｯ遘ｯ; 逕ｨ as + in_need 隗｣蜀ｳ蜀ｲ遯―n  where   竊・霍ｯ蠕・ｸ雁推闃らせ where 逕ｨ AND 諡ｼ謗･\n  order   竊・謨ｰ扈・潔菴咲ｽｮ螳壻ｼ伜・郤ｧ(蟇ｹ雎｡ {<field>: asc/desc/revert, ...}; 蜈∬ｮｸ螟夐醗); 謌・{all: asc/desc/revert} 蜈ｨ螻謖・ｻ､\n  offset  竊・additive (+); 螟壽ｬ｡螢ｰ譏守畑 + 荳ｲ謗･\n  limit   竊・last-wins\n\nas + in_need 蛻ｫ蜷榊・莠ｫ譛ｺ蛻ｶ:\n  as: 'ab'                竊・蟄鈴擇蛻ｫ蜷・ 霍ｯ蠕・ｴｯ遘ｯ譌ｶ驥榊錐諡堤ｻ・鮟倩ｮ､ in_need=false)\n  as: 'ab', in_need: true 竊・驥榊錐譌ｶ謾ｾ蠑・悽谺｡雍｡迪ｮ(逕ｨ莠手ｷｨ provider 蜈ｱ莠ｫ蜷御ｸ join/field)\n  as: '${ref:my_id}'      竊・蠑墓梼閾ｪ蜉ｨ蛻・・蜚ｯ荳蛻ｫ蜷・ 騾夊ｿ・${ref:my_id} 蝨ｨ蜈ｶ莉紋ｽ咲ｽｮ蠑慕畑\n\nList 蜉ｨ諤・｡ｹ逧・ｸ､遘肴焚謐ｮ貅・\n  sql 讓｡蠑・(data_var 譏ｾ蠑冗ｻ大ｮ・:\n    SQL 豈剰｡・= 荳鬘ｹ child; ${<data_var>.<col>(.<sub>)*} 蜿・SQL 蛻・謾ｯ謖∝ｵ悟･・JSON 蛻・\n  delegate 讓｡蠑・(child_var 譏ｾ蠑冗ｻ大ｮ・:\n    隹・岼譬・ProviderCall list_children; ${<child_var>.name/provider/meta.X} 蜿・ChildEntry 蟄玲ｮｵ\n\nResolve 蜈ｨ驛ｨ謖画ｭ｣蛻吝源驟・郤ｯ蟄鈴擇驥乗弍遨ｺ蜈・ｭ礼ｬｦ逧・粋豕募ｭ宣寔); resolve 蟄玲ｮｵ逶ｴ謗･譏ｯ <regex>: ProviderInvocation 譏蟆・ 譌 entries 蛹・｣・りｿ占｡梧悄隗｣譫宣｡ｺ蠎・\n  1) regex resolve 竊・2) 髱呎・list 蟄鈴擇 竊・3) 蜉ｨ諤・list 蜿肴衍(鮟倩ｮ､蠑蜷ｯ, 蜻ｽ荳ｭ霑・LRU)\n\nResolve 蜉霓ｽ譛溽｢ｰ謦樊｣譟･:\n  - 豈乗擅豁｣蛻・vs 髱呎・list key 蟄鈴擇驥・ 莉ｻ荳蛹ｹ驟・竊・諡堤ｻ拿n  - 豁｣蛻・vs 豁｣蛻・ regex_automata 豎ゆｺ､髮・竊・髱樒ｩｺ蛻呎拠扈拿n  - 蜉ｨ諤・list 荳榊盾荳守｢ｰ謦樊｣譟･(霑占｡梧悄遒ｰ謦樊潔隗｣譫宣｡ｺ蠎剰ｦ・・, 髱樊ｭ｣遑ｮ諤ｧ謨・囿)\n\n讓｡譚ｿ蜿倬㍼ ${...} 隸ｭ荵・隸ｦ隗・RULES.md ﾂｧ6):\n  - ${<ns>(.<path>)*}      蜻ｽ蜷咲ｩｺ髣ｴ蜿門ｼ(properties / capture / data_var / child_var / composed)\n  - ${<ns>[<N>]}           邏｢蠑戊ｮｿ髣ｮ(capture)\n  - ${<method>:<arg>}      譁ｹ豕墓・ｮｰ 窶・蠖灘燕莉・${ref:<ident>} 蠑墓梼蛻・・蛻ｫ蜷構n\nDynamicListEntry.provider 蟄玲ｮｵ隸ｭ荵・\n  - 郛ｺ逵・         竊・蠖灘燕螻ゆｸ肴撃 provider(鮟倩ｮ､; 螟ｧ螟壽焚霍ｯ逕ｱ螢ｳ襍ｰ霑呎擅)\n  - ProviderName  竊・譏ｾ蠑乗桷騾蜻ｽ蜷・provider, 逕ｨ properties 莨蜿・n  - ${child_var.provider} 竊・騾丈ｼ delegate 謨ｰ謐ｮ貅占ｿ泌屓逧・child.provider (莉・delegate 讓｡蠑・",

    "type": "object",
    "required": ["name"],
    "additionalProperties": false,
    "properties": {
        "$schema": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Schema 髞夂せ(蟒ｺ隶ｮ './schema.json5' 蜷ｯ逕ｨ IDE 陦･蜈ｨ)"
        },
        "namespace": {
            "$ref": "#/definitions/Namespace",
            "description": "蜻ｽ蜷咲ｩｺ髣ｴ(Java 蛹・｣取ｼ轤ｹ蛻・ｼ・ 郛ｺ逵・root)縲ょ・螻蜷・= <namespace>.<name>"
        },
        "name": {
            "$ref": "#/definitions/SimpleName",
            "description": "譛ｬ provider 蝨ｨ謇螻・namespace 蜀・噪邂蜊募錐(snake_case, 荳榊性轤ｹ)"
        },
        "properties": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": { "$ref": "#/definitions/PropertyDecl" },
            "description": "螻樊ｧ遲ｾ蜷・窶・隹・畑譁ｹ蝨ｨ ProviderInvocation.properties 荳ｭ襍句ｼ"
        },
        "query": { "$ref": "#/definitions/Query" },
        "list": { "$ref": "#/definitions/List" },
        "resolve": { "$ref": "#/definitions/Resolve" },
        "note": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "VD 隸ｴ譏取枚莉ｶ蜀・ｮｹ(Provider::get_note)"
        }
    },

    "definitions": {

        "ProviderName": {
            "type": "string",
            "pattern": "^[a-z][a-z0-9_]*(\\.[a-z][a-z0-9_]*)*$",
            "description": "Provider 蠑慕畑蜷・ 邂蜊募錐(蜷・namespace 蜀・衍謇ｾ) 謌也ｻ晏ｯｹ蜷・'a.b.c.name'縲ょｼ墓梼謖牙ｽ灘燕 namespace 竊・辷ｶ namespace 竊・... 竊・root 騾千ｺｧ隗｣譫・
        },

        "SimpleName": {
            "type": "string",
            "pattern": "^[a-z][a-z0-9_]*$",
            "description": "蜊墓ｮｵ譬・ｯ・ｬｦ(snake_case, 荳榊性轤ｹ)"
        },

        "Namespace": {
            "type": "string",
            "pattern": "^[a-z][a-z0-9_]*(\\.[a-z][a-z0-9_]*)*$",
            "description": "Java 蛹・｣取ｼ蜻ｽ蜷咲ｩｺ髣ｴ; 轤ｹ蛻・囈螟壽ｮｵ"
        },

        "TemplateExpr": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "蜿ｯ蜷ｫ ${...} 謠貞ｼ逧・ｭ礼ｬｦ荳ｲ縲りｯｦ隗・｡ｶ螻・description 讓｡譚ｿ蜿倬㍼蛻苓｡ｨ"
        },

        "TemplateValue": {
            "oneOf": [
                { "type": "string" },
                { "type": "number" },
                { "type": "boolean" }
            ],
            "description": "螻樊ｧ蛟ｼ蟄鈴擇驥乗・讓｡譚ｿ蟄礼ｬｦ荳ｲ(謖・PropertyDecl.type 蛛夐嚼蠑剰ｽｬ謐｢)"
        },

        "SqlExpr": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "蜿・sqlparser 譬｡鬪檎噪 SQL 迚・ｮｵ; 螟夊ｯｭ蜿･ / DDL 蝨ｨ蜉霓ｽ譛滓拠扈・
        },

        "MetaValue": {
            "description": "ChildEntry.meta 蟄玲ｮｵ蛟ｼ; 莉ｻ諢・JSON 邀ｻ蝙九りｯｦ隗・RULES.md ﾂｧ4.5縲・n  - 蟄礼ｬｦ荳ｲ + 蜷ｫ SELECT/FROM 蜈ｳ髞ｮ蟄・竊・隗・ｸｺ蜊戊｡・SELECT, 蠑墓梼謇ｧ陦悟錘蜿夜ｦ冶｡圭n  - 蟄礼ｬｦ荳ｲ + 莉・性 ${...} 讓｡譚ｿ 竊・讓｡譚ｿ謠貞ｼ, 扈捺棡菴應ｸｺ meta\n  - 蟇ｹ雎｡/謨ｰ扈・竊・騾貞ｽ貞ｯｹ豈丈ｸｪ蛟ｼ蛛壽ｨ｡譚ｿ謠貞ｼ\n  - 謨ｰ蟄・蟶・ｰ・null 竊・逶ｴ謗･菴應ｸｺ meta"
        },

        "ChildRefProvider": {
            "type": "string",
            "pattern": "^\\$\\{[a-z_][a-z0-9_]*\\.provider\\}$",
            "description": "蟇ｹ delegate 讓｡蠑・child.provider 逧・紛菴灘ｯｹ雎｡蠑慕畑; 莉・DynamicListEntry_Delegate.provider 蟄玲ｮｵ菴咲ｽｮ蜷域ｳ輔ょｽ｢螯・${<child_var>.provider}"
        },

        "Identifier": {
            "type": "string",
            "pattern": "^[a-z_][a-z0-9_]*$",
            "description": "譬・ｯ・ｬｦ(snake_case); 逕ｨ菴・child_var / data_var 遲臥ｻ大ｮ壼錐"
        },

        "PropertyDecl": {
            "oneOf": [
                { "$ref": "#/definitions/NumberProp" },
                { "$ref": "#/definitions/StringProp" },
                { "$ref": "#/definitions/BooleanProp" }
            ],
            "description": "螻樊ｧ螢ｰ譏・窶・逕ｱ type 蟄玲ｮｵ蛻､蛻ｫ"
        },

        "NumberProp": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "required": ["type"],
            "properties": {
                "type": { "const": "number" },
                "default": { "type": "number" },
                "optional": { "type": "boolean" },
                "min": { "type": "number" },
                "max": { "type": "number" }
            }
        },

        "StringProp": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "required": ["type"],
            "properties": {
                "type": { "const": "string" },
                "default": { "type": "string" },
                "optional": { "type": "boolean" },
                "pattern": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "豁｣蛻咏ｺｦ譚・
                }
            }
        },

        "BooleanProp": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "required": ["type"],
            "properties": {
                "type": { "const": "boolean" },
                "default": { "type": "boolean" },
                "optional": { "type": "boolean" }
            }
        },

        "Query": {
            "oneOf": [
                { "$ref": "#/definitions/DelegateQuery" },
                { "$ref": "#/definitions/ContribQuery" }
            ],
            "description": "闃らせ蟇ｹ邏ｯ遘ｯ ImageQuery 逧・ｴ｡迪ｮ 窶・DelegateQuery 竓・ContribQuery (presence-based)縲・n豕ｨ諢・ query.delegate 譏ｯ [蟋疲汚蜿ｦ荳 provider 逧・ｴ｡迪ｮ] (螳樔ｾ句喧逶ｮ譬・錘隹・ｮ・噪 apply_query); 荳・list[key].delegate 逧・[謨ｰ謐ｮ貅・ProviderCall] 隸ｭ荵我ｸ榊酔"
        },

        "DelegateQuery": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "required": ["delegate"],
            "properties": {
                "delegate": { "$ref": "#/definitions/ProviderCall" }
            },
            "description": "蟋疲汚蜿ｦ荳荳ｪ provider 逧・ｴ｡迪ｮ 窶・螳樔ｾ句喧逶ｮ譬・provider 蜷手ｰ・ｮ・噪 apply_query"
        },

        "ContribQuery": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "not": { "required": ["delegate"] },
            "properties": {
                "fields": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": { "$ref": "#/definitions/Field" },
                    "description": "SELECT 蛻苓ｴ｡迪ｮ(GraphQL 鬟取ｼ邏ｯ遘ｯ)縲ら畑 as + in_need 隗｣蜀ｳ霍ｯ蠕・ｸ顔噪蜻ｽ蜷榊・遯・
                },
                "from": {
                    "$ref": "#/definitions/SqlExpr",
                    "description": "FROM 蜷守噪蝓ｺ遑陦ｨ霎ｾ蠑上Ｄascading-replace 隸ｭ荵・ 荳谺｡螢ｰ譏主ｽｱ蜩堺ｸ区ｸｸ謇譛芽鰍轤ｹ; 蟄占鰍轤ｹ蜿ｯ驥榊｣ｰ譏手ｦ・尠"
                },
                "join": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": { "$ref": "#/definitions/Join" },
                    "description": "JOIN 雍｡迪ｮ(邏ｯ遘ｯ)縲よｯ城｡ｹ謖・ｮ・table + as; 逕ｨ as + in_need 隗｣蜀ｳ蜀ｲ遯・/ 霍ｨ provider 蜈ｱ莠ｫ"
                },
                "where": {
                    "$ref": "#/definitions/SqlExpr",
                    "description": "莉ｻ諢・WHERE 陦ｨ霎ｾ蠑・蜊墓擅; 蜿ｯ蜀・'a > 1 and b < 2' 遲・縲りｷｯ蠕・ｸ雁推 provider 逧・where 蠑墓梼逕ｨ AND 諡ｼ謗･"
                },
                "order": {
                    "oneOf": [
                        {
                            "type": "array",
                            "items": { "$ref": "#/definitions/OrderArrayItem" },
                            "description": "蠖｢諤・A: 謨ｰ扈・潔菴咲ｽｮ螳壻ｼ伜・郤ｧ(菴・index 莨伜・)縲よｯ城｡ｹ譏ｯ {<field>: 'asc'|'desc'|'revert'} 蜊暮醗蟇ｹ雎｡; 'revert' 鄙ｻ霓ｬ隸･蟄玲ｮｵ荳頑ｸｸ蟾ｲ螢ｰ譏守噪譁ｹ蜷・ 蜷悟錐蟄玲ｮｵ蜷主｣ｰ譏手ｦ・尠蜑榊｣ｰ譏・荳肴冠髞・"
                        },
                        { "$ref": "#/definitions/OrderGlobal" }
                    ],
                    "description": "ORDER BY 雍｡迪ｮ; 莠碁我ｸ: 謨ｰ扈・菴咲ｽｮ螳壼ｺ・ 竓・{all:...} 蜈ｨ螻謖・ｻ､"
                },
                "offset": {
                    "oneOf": [
                        { "type": "number" },
                        { "$ref": "#/definitions/TemplateExpr" }
                    ],
                    "description": "OFFSET 蛟ｼ; 謨ｰ蟄怜ｭ鈴擇驥乗・讓｡譚ｿ蟄礼ｬｦ荳ｲ縲りｷｯ蠕・ｴｯ遘ｯ隸ｭ荵・ 螟壻ｸｪ provider 蜷・・螢ｰ譏惹ｼ夊｢ｫ蠑墓梼逕ｨ + 荳ｲ謗･荳ｺ (o1) + (o2) + ...(蠏悟･怜・鬘ｵ)"
                },
                "limit": {
                    "oneOf": [
                        { "type": "number" },
                        { "$ref": "#/definitions/TemplateExpr" }
                    ],
                    "description": "LIMIT 蛟ｼ; 謨ｰ蟄怜ｭ鈴擇驥乗・讓｡譚ｿ蟄礼ｬｦ荳ｲ縲りｷｯ蠕・ｴｯ遘ｯ隸ｭ荵・ last-wins(譛ｫ谺｡螢ｰ譏手・)縲Ｍimit:0 = 遨ｺ髮・SQL 閾ｪ辟ｶ陦御ｸｺ, 荳咲音谿雁喧)"
                }
            }
        },

        "Field": {
            "oneOf": [
                { "$ref": "#/definitions/SqlExpr" },
                { "$ref": "#/definitions/FieldObject" }
            ],
            "description": "SELECT field. Bare string is shorthand for {sql:<string>}; object form supports as/in_need."
        },

        "FieldObject": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "required": ["sql"],
            "properties": {
                "sql": { "$ref": "#/definitions/SqlExpr" },
                "as": { "$ref": "#/definitions/AliasName" },
                "in_need": { "type": "boolean" }
            }
        },

        "Join": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "required": ["table", "as"],
            "properties": {
                "kind": {
                    "enum": ["INNER", "LEFT", "RIGHT", "FULL"],
                    "description": "JOIN 邀ｻ蝙・ 鮟倩ｮ､ INNER"
                },
                "table": {
                    "$ref": "#/definitions/SqlExpr",
                    "description": "逶ｮ譬・｡ｨ蜷肴・蟄先衍隸｢縲Ｆ.g. 'album_images' / '(SELECT id, ts FROM ...)'"
                },
                "as": {
                    "$ref": "#/definitions/AliasName",
                    "description": "陦ｨ蛻ｫ蜷・ 蟄鈴擇驥・/ ${ref:<ident>} 閾ｪ蜉ｨ蛻・・"
                },
                "on": {
                    "$ref": "#/definitions/SqlExpr",
                    "description": "ON 蟄仙唱; 蜿ｯ蠑慕畑 ${ref:<ident>} 遲峨Ｆ.g. 'ai.image_id = images.id'"
                },
                "in_need": {
                    "type": "boolean",
                    "description": "true: 霍ｯ蠕・ｸ雁酔蜷・as 蟾ｲ蟄伜惠譌ｶ謾ｾ蠑・悽雍｡迪ｮ(霍ｨ provider 蜈ｱ莠ｫ join 逕ｨ); 鮟倩ｮ､ false: 驥榊錐謚･髞・
                }
            }
        },

        "OrderArrayItem": {
            "type": "object",
            "minProperties": 1,
            "additionalProperties": {
                "enum": ["asc", "desc", "revert"]
            },
            "description": "Order 謨ｰ扈・｡ｹ 窶・蟇ｹ雎｡ {<field_name>: 'asc'|'desc'|'revert', ...}縲ょ・隶ｸ螟夐醗; field_name 譏ｯ莉ｻ諢・SQL 蛻苓｡ｨ霎ｾ蠑・蜿ｯ蜷ｫ陦ｨ蜑咲ｼ螯・'images.crawled_at'); 'revert' 陦ｨ遉ｺ鄙ｻ霓ｬ隸･蟄玲ｮｵ蝨ｨ荳頑ｸｸ逧・婿蜷・ 荳頑ｸｸ譛ｪ螢ｰ譏主・隗・ｸｺ譁ｰ蠅槭ょ､夐醗譌ｶ髞ｮ髣ｴ莨伜・郤ｧ謖牙｣ｰ譏朱｡ｺ蠎上・
        },

        "OrderGlobal": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "required": ["all"],
            "properties": {
                "all": {
                    "enum": ["asc", "desc", "revert"],
                    "description": "蜈ｨ螻謖・ｻ､蟇ｹ謇譛我ｸ頑ｸｸ order 蟄玲ｮｵ逕滓譜: 'revert' = 鄙ｻ霓ｬ ASC竊妊ESC; 'asc'/'desc' = 蠑ｺ蛻ｶ扈滉ｸ譁ｹ蜷・
                }
            },
            "description": "Order 蜈ｨ螻謖・ｻ､ {all: 'asc'|'desc'|'revert'}; 蠎皮畑譌ｶ謠貞・邏ｯ遘ｯ體ｾ鬘ｶ, 蠖ｱ蜩堺ｸ区ｸｸ謇譛芽鰍轤ｹ逧・婿蜷題ｧ｣驥・
        },

        "AliasName": {
            "oneOf": [
                {
                    "type": "string",
                    "pattern": "^[a-z_][a-z0-9_]*$",
                    "description": "蟄鈴擇蛻ｫ蜷・snake_case)"
                },
                { "$ref": "#/definitions/RefAlias" }
            ],
            "description": "蛻ｫ蜷・ 蟄鈴擇驥・snake_case) / ${ref:<ident>} 蠑墓梼閾ｪ蜉ｨ蛻・・"
        },

        "RefAlias": {
            "type": "string",
            "pattern": "^\\$\\{ref:[a-z_][a-z0-9_]*\\}$",
            "description": "蠑墓梼閾ｪ蜉ｨ蛻・・蛻ｫ蜷榊頃菴咲ｬｦ縲ょ酔 ident 蝨ｨ query 蜀・・莉紋ｽ咲ｽｮ(螯・join.on / where) 逕ｨ ${ref:<ident>} 蠑慕畑"
        },

        "List": {
            "type": "object",
            "patternProperties": {
                ".*\\$\\{[a-z_][a-z0-9_]*(?:\\.[a-z_][a-z0-9_]*)+\\}.*": {
                    "$ref": "#/definitions/DynamicListEntry",
                    "description": "蜉ｨ諤・｡ｹ: key 蜷ｫ ${ident.field}, 蠢・｡ｻ譛・sql 謌・delegate 菴應ｸｺ謨ｰ謐ｮ貅・
                },
                "^(?!.*\\$\\{).+$": {
                    "$ref": "#/definitions/StaticListEntry",
                    "description": "髱呎・｡ｹ: key 蟄鈴擇驥・ 逕ｨ ProviderInvocation 莠梧・
                }
            },
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "description": "蟄占鰍轤ｹ譫壻ｸｾ 窶・髱呎∝ｭ鈴擇驥・key 謌・蜷ｫ ${ident.field} 逧・勘諤・key"
        },

        "StaticListEntry": {
            "$ref": "#/definitions/ProviderInvocation",
            "description": "髱呎・list 鬘ｹ = ProviderInvocation 莠梧・(byName / Empty); 6e 襍ｷ byDelegate variant 蟾ｲ蛻髯､"
        },

        "DynamicListEntry": {
            "oneOf": [
                { "$ref": "#/definitions/DynamicListEntry_Sql" },
                { "$ref": "#/definitions/DynamicListEntry_Delegate" }
            ],
            "description": "蜉ｨ諤・list 鬘ｹ 窶・謨ｰ謐ｮ貅蝉ｺ呈箕: sql 竓・delegate"
        },

        "DynamicListEntry_Sql": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "required": ["sql", "data_var"],
            "not": { "required": ["delegate", "child_var"] },
            "properties": {
                "sql": {
                    "$ref": "#/definitions/SqlExpr",
                    "description": "謨ｰ謐ｮ貅・SQL; 騾壼ｸｸ蜷ｫ ${composed} 蟄先衍隸｢縲よｯ剰｡・= 荳鬘ｹ child; 騾夊ｿ・${<data_var>.<col>} 蜿・SQL 蛻・
                },
                "data_var": {
                    "$ref": "#/definitions/Identifier",
                    "description": "SQL 陦檎ｻ大ｮ壼錐縲ょｼ墓梼隕∵ｱ・key 荳・properties 荳ｭ謇譛・${X.Y} 逧・X 蠢・｡ｻ遲我ｺ取ｭ､蛟ｼ"
                },
                "provider": {
                    "$ref": "#/definitions/ProviderName",
                    "description": "郛ｺ逵・荳肴撃 provider; 蟄礼ｬｦ荳ｲ=譏ｾ蠑丞多蜷・(SQL 讓｡蠑乗裏騾丈ｼ)"
                },
                "properties": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "additionalProperties": { "$ref": "#/definitions/TemplateValue" },
                    "description": "莨扈吝ｽ灘燕螻・provider 逧・ｱ樊ｧ; 蛟ｼ蜿ｯ蜷ｫ ${<data_var>.<col>} 蠑慕畑"
                },
                "meta": {
                    "$ref": "#/definitions/MetaValue",
                    "description": "蜿ｯ騾・meta(豈剰｡梧鴬陦御ｸ谺｡); 隗・RULES.md ﾂｧ4.5縲ょ庄荳ｺ SQL 蟄礼ｬｦ荳ｲ(隶ｿ髣ｮ ${data_var.col}) / ${data_var}(騾丈ｼ謨ｴ陦・ / 蜷ｫ讓｡譚ｿ逧・ｯｹ雎｡"
                }
            }
        },

        "DynamicListEntry_Delegate": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "required": ["delegate", "child_var"],
            "not": { "required": ["sql", "data_var"] },
            "properties": {
                "delegate": {
                    "$ref": "#/definitions/ProviderCall",
                    "description": "謨ｰ謐ｮ貅・provider 蠑慕畑; 螳樔ｾ句喧蜷手ｰ・ｮ・噪 list_children, 豈丈ｸｪ child = 荳鬘ｹ縲る夊ｿ・${<child_var>.name} / ${<child_var>.provider} / ${<child_var>.meta.X} 蜿・ChildEntry 蟄玲ｮｵ"
                },
                "child_var": {
                    "$ref": "#/definitions/Identifier",
                    "description": "ChildEntry 扈大ｮ壼錐縲ょｼ墓梼隕∵ｱ・key 荳・properties 荳ｭ謇譛・${X.Y} 逧・X 蠢・｡ｻ遲我ｺ取ｭ､蛟ｼ"
                },
                "provider": {
                    "oneOf": [
                        { "$ref": "#/definitions/ProviderName" },
                        { "$ref": "#/definitions/ChildRefProvider" }
                    ],
                    "description": "郛ｺ逵・荳肴撃 provider(鮟倩ｮ､; provider蟶ｸ隗・; 蟄礼ｬｦ荳ｲ=譏ｾ蠑乗桷騾(霍ｯ逕ｱ螢ｳ蟶ｸ隗・; ${<child_var>.provider}=騾丈ｼ delegate 霑泌屓逧・child.provider"
                },
                "properties": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "additionalProperties": { "$ref": "#/definitions/TemplateValue" },
                    "description": "莨扈吝ｽ灘燕螻・provider 逧・ｱ樊ｧ; 蛟ｼ蜿ｯ蜷ｫ ${<child_var>.name|provider|meta.X} 蠑慕畑"
                },
                "meta": {
                    "$ref": "#/definitions/MetaValue",
                    "description": "蜿ｯ騾・meta(豈丈ｸｪ child 謇ｧ陦御ｸ谺｡); 隗・RULES.md ﾂｧ4.5縲ょ庄荳ｺ SQL 蟄礼ｬｦ荳ｲ(隶ｿ髣ｮ ${child_var.X}) / ${child_var.meta}(騾丈ｼ荳雁ｱ・meta) / 蜷ｫ讓｡譚ｿ逧・ｯｹ雎｡"
                }
            }
        },

        "Resolve": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": { "$ref": "#/definitions/ProviderInvocation" },
            "description": "豁｣蛻・竊・ProviderInvocation 譏蟆・(逶ｴ謗･ key-value, 譌 entries 蛹・｣・縲よ園譛・key 荳蠕区潔豁｣蛻咏ｼ冶ｯ・(郤ｯ蟄鈴擇驥乗弍遨ｺ蜈・ｭ礼ｬｦ逧・粋豕募ｭ宣寔)縲・n\nKey 蠖｢諤・(7b 襍ｷ):\n  - 髱呎・regex (譌 ${...})         竊・蜉霓ｽ譛溽ｼ冶ｯ曾n  - instance-static (${properties.X}) 竊・螳樔ｾ句喧譛滓ｸｲ譟灘錘蜀咲ｼ冶ｯ曾n  - 荳榊・隶ｸ ${data_var.X} / ${child_var.X} (resolve 陦ｨ譌 row/child 荳贋ｸ区枚)\n\n霑占｡梧悄隗｣譫宣｡ｺ蠎・(deterministic): regex resolve 竊・髱呎・list 蟄鈴擇 竊・蜉ｨ諤・list 蜿肴衍 (鮟倩ｮ､蠑蜷ｯ)縲・n\n7b 襍ｷ: 蠑墓梼荳榊・蛛壼刈霓ｽ譛溽｢ｰ謦樊｣豬・窶・`.*` 霓ｬ蜿第ｨ｡蠑・+ instance-static key 驛ｽ隶ｩ隸･譽豬句・譏ｯ false-positive縲ょ､壽ｨ｡蠑城㍾蜿逕ｱ菴懆・潔 schema 蜃ｺ邇ｰ鬘ｺ蠎剰ｦ・・蜀ｳ螳壹・
        },

        "ProviderInvocation": {
            "oneOf": [
                { "$ref": "#/definitions/InvokeByName" },
                { "$ref": "#/definitions/InvokeByDelegate" },
                { "$ref": "#/definitions/EmptyInvocation" }
            ],
            "description": "荳画・(7b 襍ｷ):\n  - InvokeByName  窶・`{provider, properties?, meta?}`; 螳樔ｾ句喧 provider, 螳・叉荳ｺ resolve 扈捺棡\n  - InvokeByDelegate 窶・`{delegate: ProviderCall, meta?}`; 螳樔ｾ句喧 ProviderCall.provider, 隹・target.resolve(name) 霓ｬ蜿・ target 扈吝・逧・・螻・provider 荳ｺ扈捺棡 (莉・Resolve 陦ｨ譛画譜; 髱呎・list 鬘ｹ荳榊・隶ｸ)\n  - EmptyInvocation 窶・`{meta?}` 蜊菴構n\n逕ｨ莠・StaticListEntry (莉・ByName / Empty) 荳・Resolve 鬘ｹ (荳画∝・蜈∬ｮｸ)縲・n\nInvokeByDelegate 譏ｯ 7b 陦･蝗樒噪 窶・query.delegate / list[].delegate / resolve[].delegate 荳牙､・delegate 蠖｢謌仙ｯｹ遘ｰ: 豈丈ｸｪ驛ｽ'隹・畑蜈ｶ荳贋ｸ区枚蟇ｹ蠎皮噪謫堺ｽ懷ｹｶ霓ｬ蜿・縲・
        },

        "InvokeByName": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "required": ["provider"],
            "not": { "required": ["delegate"] },
            "properties": {
                "provider": { "$ref": "#/definitions/ProviderName" },
                "properties": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "additionalProperties": { "$ref": "#/definitions/TemplateValue" }
                },
                "meta": { "$ref": "#/definitions/MetaValue" }
            }
        },

        "InvokeByDelegate": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "required": ["delegate"],
            "not": { "required": ["provider"] },
            "properties": {
                "delegate": {
                    "$ref": "#/definitions/ProviderCall",
                    "description": "[謫堺ｽ懆ｽｬ蜿・窶・蟇ｹ遘ｰ隸ｭ荵云 螳樔ｾ句喧 ProviderCall.provider; 蝨ｨ蜈ｶ荳願ｰ・畑豁､荳贋ｸ区枚蟇ｹ蠎疲婿豕・(resolve 陦ｨ驥・竊・target.resolve(name)). 荳・query.delegate (竊・target.apply_query) / DynamicListEntry_Delegate.delegate (竊・target.list) 蠖｢謌蝉ｸ牙､・ｯｹ遘ｰ"
                },
                "meta": { "$ref": "#/definitions/MetaValue" }
            },
            "description": "Resolve 陦ｨ鬘ｹ逧・ByDelegate 蠖｢諤・窶・7b 陦･蝗槭ゆｻ・Resolve 陦ｨ譛画譜; 髱呎・list 鬘ｹ荳榊・隶ｸ (蝗 list 鬘ｹ隕∵ｱりｿ泌屓 ChildEntry, 霓ｬ蜿題ｯｭ荵我ｸ咲ｻ・粋)"
        },

        "ProviderCall": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "required": ["provider"],
            "properties": {
                "provider": { "$ref": "#/definitions/ProviderName" },
                "properties": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "additionalProperties": { "$ref": "#/definitions/TemplateValue" },
                    "description": "莨扈咏岼譬・provider 逧・ｱ樊ｧ隕・尠蛟ｼ"
                }
            },
            "description": "蟇ｹ蜿ｦ荳荳ｪ provider 逧・ｼ慕畑 (蜷ｫ properties); 逕ｨ莠・query.delegate / DynamicListEntry_Delegate.delegate"
        },

        "EmptyInvocation": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "not": {
                "anyOf": [
                    { "required": ["provider"] },
                    { "required": ["delegate"] },
                    { "required": ["properties"] }
                ]
            },
            "properties": {
                "meta": { "$ref": "#/definitions/MetaValue" }
            },
            "description": "遨ｺ invocation: 譌 provider 荵滓裏 delegate縲りｷｯ蠕・ｻ咲・蟶ｸ郛灘ｭ・ 菴・ｼ墓梼荳榊惠隸･蟄占鰍轤ｹ謠蝉ｾ・list / resolve 譛榊苅(郛灘ｭ倬｡ｹ荳ｺ遨ｺ, meta 蜿ｯ騾・"
        }

    }
}
